# Cloudflare Pages response headers (docs/SmartCrop_PDF_Specification_Web.md §7.1, ARCHITECTURE.md
# §18). Cross-origin isolation (COOP+COEP) is what makes crossOriginIsolated true, which is what
# lets ONNX Runtime Web's wasm execution provider use multiple threads instead of one
# (dewarp.ts::resolve_onnx_execution_providers) — every asset this app loads is same-origin, so
# require-corp has nothing to block here.
/*
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
  Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy: require-corp
